# HUD::SHOW_TICK_ON_BLIP

## Summary
Shows a tick indicator on this blip

## Parameters
* **BLIP_INDEX** blip
* **BOOL** showTick

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Adds a green checkmark on top of a blip.
